Watch the official music video for "Somewhere In My Heart" by Aztec Camera. "Somewhere in My Heart" is the twelfth single and biggest hit by the Scottish band. It was released as the third single from their 1987 studio album "Love". The song was produced by Michael Jonzun and written by Roddy Frame. 

The music video was directed by John Scarlett-Davis and produced by Nick Verden for Radar Films.

